@startuml Deployment
title Containerized NoSQL Environment

node "Docker Host" {
    cloud "External Request (Port 5002)" as Ext
    
    package "Docker Network: notes-network" {
        component [Frontend Container\n(notes-frontend)] as FE
        component [Backend Container\n(notes-backend)] as BE
        component [Database Container\n(notes-mongodb)] as DB
        
        storage "mongodb_data" as Vol
    }
}

Ext --> FE: HTTP/S
FE --> BE: Internal REST API (Port 3000)
BE --> DB: MongoDB Protocol (Port 27017)
DB -down-> Vol: Persistent Storage
@enduml
